issues.title: option_test fails with g++ 7 -std=c++1z
issues.body:
Please compile with -fno-new-ttp-matching .
I'll fix it later.

>The resolution of DR 150 on matching of template template parameters, allowing default template arguments to make a template match a parameter, is currently enabled by default in C++17 mode only. The default can be overridden with -f{no-,}new-ttp-matching.

commit.message: fix test for new stream api
break backward compatibility of cybozu::stream::readSome -> cybozu::readSome
serializer.hpp does not depend on string.hpp
inline is necessary for template specialization
thread safe of RandomGenerator::read for vc
add detection of aarch64 little endian
fix error of hash on Mac
fix detection of version of gcc 5.4
don't check sd_ with FD_SETSIZE on Windows
add comment to check iv len
use std instead of tr1 for clang on mac
rename macro name to use epoll
rename setBlock to setBlocking and change param
fix bug; read() will block if readSize is zero
git st! second parameter of RandomGenerator::read() is the number of elements
check argc whether positive or not
add Option::setDelimiter to stop parsing after delimiter
add output format of online for stacktrace
append -e option and load text from file
consider an environment without boost, mecab
add throw() for Log() and Logger()
use old fp if open fails
call toString in cstr of Exception
fix macro error if __GNUC_PREREQ is not defined
Bfd class runs well on valgrind
doClear is a parameter of AlignedArray::resize
expand size of rand for vc
use FILE for /dev/urandom to get speed
remove operator== for SocketAddr ; add hasSameAddr
avoid warning of comparision of integers of different signs
fix bug of setTimeout on Linux
avoid error of vc with max/min macro
break backward compatibility ; change FileInfo.isFile to method ; remove '.', '..' in FileList
move __attribute__ to definition ; use _Printf_format_string_ for VC
default key is moved to parameter
use attribute for format if gcc
add comma before message of help
remove old-style cast in some files
cybozu::Option integer parser support hex integer
Event with mutex and condition_variable for c++11
